        <item>
            <title>煮食计时成 Vision Pro「杀手级 App」   外媒：办公方面有待提升</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/11/apple-vision-pro-best-usage-is-timer-in-kitchen-said-foreign-press/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-vision-pro-best-usage-is-timer-in-kitchen-said-foreign-press</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/11/apple-vision-pro-best-usage-is-timer-in-kitchen-said-foreign-press/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 10:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AR/VR]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1218896</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple Vision Pro 上周于美国市场正式发售，尽管其售价不菲，但当其开放预订后半小时内就被抢购一空，据外媒估计，Apple 已售出逾 20 万个 Vision Pro。日前《The Wall Street Journal》资深记者 Joanna Stern 就表示：「最近用 Apple Vision Pro 做过最实用的事，就是煮食时在锅上设置悬浮虚拟计时器。」</p><p>《The Wall Street Journal》资深记者 Joanna Stern 日前头戴 Vision Pro 出席 CNBC 的访谈节目，并在节目中分享其试用 Apple Vision Pro 的感受。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionproreview-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionproreview-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/applevisionproreview-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dfbgNPk2nwk&amp;ab_channel=CNBCTelevision">CNBC Television@YouTube</a></p><p>Joanna Stern 表示，自从她发现 Vision Pro 可以用作厨房的计时器，而且可以「放在」任何地方之时，她觉得自己就如真正置身未来。Apple Vision Pro 能够供用家建立悬浮虚拟计时器之余，借着空间追踪技术，即使用家转头查看股票价格或其他资料，只要用家回头再看，计时器会继续维持在原地。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">You won&#39;t find it in Apple&#39;s marketing but the Vision Pro is the ultimate cooking computer. Was one of the moments where I could really see the future&#8230; <a href="https://t.co/ph8n0NgUHI">pic.twitter.com/ph8n0NgUHI</a></p><p>&mdash; Joanna Stern (@JoannaStern) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoannaStern/status/1752356086311452828?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 30, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>撇除厨房计时器这个用途，外媒《Wired》报道指，Apple Vision Pro 需要利用拇指及食指轻触进行操作，然而在实际工作上这项技术大大拖慢了用家工作效率。除了用家不习惯以这种方式直接操控眼前的程式外，用家现时亦只可以用食指打字，使部分用户放弃使用虚拟键盘，转而使用传统实体键盘。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.wsj.com/tech/apple-vision-pro-review-39f2d82e">The Wall Street Journal</a>、<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/apple-vision-pro-boils-down-to-kitchen-timers-and-thats-a-problem/">Wired</a>、<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/962/962571.htm">快科技</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/10/apple-vision-pro-new-reset-function/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Vision Pro 终设重置密码功能，不必亲身到 Apple Store 维修</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/apple-vision-pro-china-launch-april/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Vision Pro 中国推出安排，供应链爆料指最快 4 月上市</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/youtube-apple-vision-pro-app-on-the-way/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Google 高层突然改口风，将开发 Apple Vision Pro 专属 YouTube 程式</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/11/apple-vision-pro-best-usage-is-timer-in-kitchen-said-foreign-press/vr-mr-ar/">煮食计时成 Vision Pro「杀手级 App」   外媒：办公方面有待提升</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
